---
interface Props {
    title: string;
    body: string;
    href: string;
}

const {href, title, body} = Astro.props;
---

<div class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl divide-y divide-brand-soft/60 px-6 py-32 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight text-brand-navy">Frequently asked questions</h2>

        <dl class="mt-10 space-y-8 divide-y divide-brand-soft/60">

            <div class="pt-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-brand-navy lg:col-span-5">
                    Do I need to be a crypto expert to join?
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-4 lg:col-span-7 lg:mt-0">
                    <p class="text-base leading-7 text-brand-navy/80">
                        Not at all. Everyone’s welcome — from curious newcomers to seasoned builders. Come learn, connect, and grow with the community.
                    </p>
                </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-brand-navy lg:col-span-5">
                    What kind of networking can I expect?
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-4 lg:col-span-7 lg:mt-0">
                    <p class="text-base leading-7 text-brand-navy/80">
                        Plenty. Each event includes time to meet founders, investors, and peers — real conversations, real connections, no pressure.
                    </p>
                </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-brand-navy lg:col-span-5">
                    What makes CryptoMondays Zurich different?
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-4 lg:col-span-7 lg:mt-0">
                    <p class="text-base leading-7 text-brand-navy/80">
                        We’re more than events — we’re a community. As the most active crypto and Web3 network in Zurich, every meetup sparks collaboration, opens new doors, and strengthens the local ecosystem.
                    </p>
                </dd>
            </div>

        </dl>
    </div>
</div>
